def is_kiss(words):

def is_kiss(words):
    return "Keep It Simple Stupid" if max(len(i) for i in words.split())>len(words.split()) else "Good work Joe!"

def is_kiss(stg):
    words = stg.split()
    l = len(words)
    return "Good work Joe!" if all(len(word) <= l for word in words) else "Keep It Simple Stupid"
